  "text": "However, BO consumes most of the transmit antenna re sources for perfect nulling so that it is difficult to obtain transmit diversity gain from the beamforming for user seg mentation. Therefore, to achieve higher diversity gain, extra antenna resources are needed as in [CITATION_1] .",
